node.text: IN ONE WEEK-Join me for a once-in-this-galaxy experience when I team up w/ Richard & Demi Weitz from RWQuarantunes for a virtual fundraising phenomenon benefiting the USC Leslie and William McMorrow Neighborhood Academic Initiative! 🥳🎇🎉 This incredible Zoom event will include performances by GREAT entertainers-visits from me & some of my favorite Star Wars pals! Go to maythe4th.usc.edu & use “TheForce” discount code to bring the $500 ticket down to $100, which is tax deductible, so DON'T MISS THE FUN! #NAI #USC #StayTuned @uscedu @rwquarantunes
